nk:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 01, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fpz1719812992669.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fpz1719812992669.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fpz1719812992669.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bia1665702602368\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $occvalidation\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bia1665702602368___occvalidation_279091\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Check whether an occurrence requires validation.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bia1665702602368__topic_d87296e1_d87297e1_d87298e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bia1665702602368__p_d87299e1_d87300e1_d87301e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bia1665702602368__topic_d58117e1_d58118e1_d58119e1_d58120e1_d58121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611356e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bia1665702602368__topic_d58122e1_d58123e1_d58124e1_d58125e1_d58126e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611356e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is not valid, for example, the field name is not drawn.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence does not require validation, either because the occurrence has not been modified or it has already been successfully modified. Check the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span> to determine which of these situations applies.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bia1665702602368__table_d9317e1_d9318e1_d9319e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence requires validation.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bia1665702602368__topic_d58127e1_d58128e1_d58129e1_d58130e1_d58131e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611356e202\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bia1665702602368__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bia1665702602368__topic_d58132e1_d58133e1_d58134e1_d58135e1_d58136e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611356e212\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bia1665702602368__p_d87317e1_d87318e1_d87319e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> enables you to check whether an occurrence requires validation. An occurrence needs validation in either of the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bia1665702602368__li_d35111e1_d35112e1_d35113e1\">Data in one of the fields of the occurrence has been modified (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span> is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> is also 1).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bia1665702602368__li_d35114e1_d35115e1_d35116e1\">Validation has been demanded by ProcScript (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span> is 1), regardless of the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bia1665702602368__section_x1t_syk_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d611356e245\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In this example <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span> returns the validation\n            status of the current occurrence of an entity.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bia1665702602368__pre_chp_tyk_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; DUMMY and FLD2 are non-database fields\n; enter an appropriate entity name in FLD2\nvEntity = $occvalidation(\"%%FLD2%%%\")\nselectcase(vEntity)\n case \"\"\n message/error \"Entity name is not valid\"\n case 0\n message/info \"The occurrence is valid\"\n case 1\n message/info \"The occurrence requires validation\"\nendselectcase\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdc1665702602510.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a field requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biz1719502191613.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancevalidation</a><p>Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hnz1719661363571.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420703\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420703\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$occvalidation Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 01, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. $occvalidation { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $occvalidation Value Meaning \"\" Entity is not valid, for example, the field name is not drawn. 0 Occurrence does not require validation, either because the occurrence has not been modified or it has already been successfully modified. Check the value of $occmod to determine which of these situations applies. 1 Occurrence requires validation. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description $occvalidation enables you to check whether an occurrence requires validation. An occurrence needs validation in either of the following circumstances: Data in one of the fields of the occurrence has been modified ( $occmod is 1), but has not yet been successfully validated ( $occvalidation is also 1). Validation has been demanded by ProcScript ( $occcheck is 1), regardless of the value of $occvalidation . Example: Using $occvalidation In this example $occvalidation returns the validation status of the current occurrence of an entity. ; DUMMY and FLD2 are non-database fields ; enter an appropriate entity name in FLD2 vEntity = $occvalidation(\"%%FLD2%%%\") selectcase(vEntity) case \"\" message/error \"Entity name is not valid\" case 0 message/info \"The occurrence is valid\" case 1 message/info \"The occurrence requires validation\" endselectcase Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validateocc Validate an occurrence. $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. $instancevalidation Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $occcheck Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}